  "prompt": "What is the best and most economic perfume for men in India?",
  "response": "The best and most economical perfume for men in India can vary based on personal preferences, but here are some popular and affordable options widely appreciated for their quality and longevity:\n\n### **1. FOGG Impressio (Series - Black, Blue, etc.)**\n   - **Price:** \u20b9300 to \u20b9500 (125 ml)\n   - **Why Choose It?** FOGG perfumes are known for their long-lasting fragrance and affordability. The Impressio series offers a variety of scents, from fresh and citrusy to woody and masculine.\n\n### **2. Wild Stone Code (Series - Titanium, Steel, etc.)**\n   - **Price:** \u20b9300 to \u20b9600 (100 ml)\n   - **Why Choose It?** Wild Stone is a trusted brand for men's grooming products. The Code series offers a range of fragrances suitable for different occasions, from casual to formal.\n\n### **3. Engage W1 (Series - Days, Nights, etc.)**\n   - **Price:** \u20b9200 to \u20b9400 (100 ml)\n   - **Why Choose It?** Engage perfumes are lightweight, fresh, and budget-friendly. They are ideal for daily wear and come in various variants like Days, Nights, and Seasons.\n\n### **4. Park Avenue Voyage**\n   - **Price:** \u20b9300 to \u20b9500 (100 ml)\n   - **Why Choose It?** Park Avenue Voyage offers a luxurious feel at an affordable price. It\u2019s known for its fresh and aquatic fragrance, making it perfect for all-day wear.\n\n### **5. Axe Signature (Series - Dark Temptation, Gold, etc.)**\n   - **Price:** \u20b9200 to \u20b9400 (150 ml)\n   - **Why Choose It?** Axe is a popular choice for young men. The Signature series provides a range of fragrances, from spicy to fresh, and is very pocket-friendly.\n\n### **6. NEO by Titan Skinn**\n   - **Price:** \u20b9500 to \u20b9700 (100 ml)\n   - **Why Choose It?** An affordable offering from the premium Titan Skinn range, NEO is a youthful and energetic fragrance with a modern touch.\n\n### **7. Yardley London (Gentleman Classic, Elite, etc.)**\n   - **Price:** \u20b9300 to \u20b9500 (100 ml)\n   - **Why Choose It?** Yardley London offers classic, sophisticated fragrances at an affordable price. It\u2019s perfect for those looking for a mature and elegant scent.\n\n### **8. Denver Hamilton**\n   - **Price:** \u20b9200 to \u20b9400 (100 ml)\n   - **Why Choose It?** Denver Hamilton is a budget-friendly option with a fresh and invigorating fragrance, ideal for daily wear.\n\n### Tips for Choosing:\n- **Try Before You Buy:** Always test a fragrance on your skin to see how it reacts with your body chemistry.\n- **Occasion Matters:** Choose lighter, fresher scents for daytime and bolder, musky fragrances for evenings or formal events.\n- **Longevity:** Check reviews for longevity, as some budget perfumes may not last as long as premium ones.\n\nThese options provide excellent value for money and are widely available in India both online (Amazon, Flipkart, Nykaa) and in local stores.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
